1993;;Life with Mikey;;American;;James Lapine;;Michael J. Fox, Christina Vidal, Cyndi Lauper, Nathan Lane;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Life_with_Mikey;;Mikey Chapman (Michael J. Fox), a former child star and now a talent agent for child stars, discovers Angie Vega (Christina Vidal, in her first movie), a girl who pick-pockets for money and lives with her teenage sister and her boyfriend. Together, they try to hit it big and earn her a role on a series of television commercials.